<P N="8"><PB N="34" REF="028354_0032_0FD8A9FE57DB6430">8 Behold, I will bring them from the North country, and gather them from the coa&s;ts of the earth: the blind and the lame, the woman with child, and her that travails with child to|gether: a great company &s;hall return hither.</P>
