<P N="33"><PB N="36" REF="028354_0034_0FD8AA0428AE2770">33. But this &s;hall be the covenant that I will make with the hou&s;e of I&s;rael; after tho&s;e days, &s;ays the Lord, I will put my law in their in|ward parts, and write it in their hearts; and I will be their God, and they &s;hall be my people.</P>
