<P N="1">1 For behold, in tho&s;e days, and in that time, when I bring again the captivity of Ju|dah to Jeru&s;alem,</P>
<P N="2">2 I will al&s;o gather all nations, and bring them down to the valley of Jeho&s;haphat, to plead with them there for my people, for I&s;rael my heritage, whom they have &s;cattered among the nations, and for dividing my land.</P>
