<P N="11">11 In that day, there &s;hall be great mourn|ing in Jeru&s;alem, like the mourning of Hadadri|mon, in the valley of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">g<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">on.</P>
